snippet.title: Midnight Ghost Hunt trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description: A 4v4 prop hunt game where the props fight back. Ghosts possesses objects, ghost hunters try to find them, and when the clock strikes midnight, the tables are turned. Find out more here: https://www.pcgamer.com/midnight-ghost-hunt-game/
